value.value: 膣の欠如
absence of the female reproductive canal located between the uterus and the vulva
膣乾燥
lack of the normal presence or reduced presence of secretions in the vagina

処女膜の欠如
absence of the thin membrane which may partially occlude the opening of the vagina
無孔処女膜
absence of the normal opening of the thin membrane which may partially occlude the opening of the vagina; here the opening is completely occluded
膣の炎症
local accumulation of fluid, plasma proteins, and leukocytes in the vagina
血管内皮細胞の発生異常
anomaly in the differentiation of the cells that line the vasculature
血管内皮細胞の分化異常
anomaly in the process whereby a relatively unspecialized cell acquires specialized features of an endothelial cell
血管内皮細胞の遊走異常

アルコール消費の上昇
greater than normal consumption of alcohol
アルコール消費の低下
less than normal consumption of alcohol
肺動脈圧の異常
altered tension of the blood within the pulmonary arteries
肺性高血圧
sustained high pulmonary pressure at a level that is likely to result in disease and/or other pathological states
肺性低血圧
sustained low pulmonary pressure at a level that is likely to result in disease and/or other pathological states

any structural anomaly of the loose fold of skin that covers the penis
包茎
inability of the penis to protrude from the prepuce/foreskin; may be due to a narrow opening of the foreskin resulting in the inability to retract the distal foreskin over the glans penis
性病索（尿道索）

輸精管の欠如

子宮の二分

骨関節炎

関節リウマチ

グルカゴンの分泌異常

anomaly in the production or release of this hormone secreted by the alpha cells of the islets of Langerhans; it normally plays a role in regulation of blood glucose concentration, ketone metabolism, and other biochemical and physiological processes
細胞接着の異常
altered ability of a cell to adhere to another cell or to a non-cellular component of the environment
胎児の心筋細胞増殖異常
anomaly in the ability of the differentiating cardiac muscle cell population to undergo expansion by cell division
子宮閉鎖症

平滑筋腫

子宮平滑筋腫
greater than the expected number of a benign tumor derived from smooth (nonstriated) muscle of the uterus, occurring in a specific population in a given time period
子宮破裂

子宮の発育異常
abnormal morphogenesis of the female muscular organ of gestation
卵管の形態異常
any structural anomaly of the tube through which the ova pass from the ovary to the uterus
卵管の欠如

卵管の発育不全

卵巣の欠如

卵巣がん発生率上昇
greater than the expected number of a malignant neoplasm arising from ovarian tissue, occurring in a specific population in a given time period
繊維腫
greater than the expected number of a benign tumor of fibrous or fully developed connective tissue, in a specific population in a given time period
卵巣繊維腫

卵巣の発育異常

輸尿管の二分

輸尿管の肥大
increased size or length of the tube that conducts the urine from the renal pelvis to the bladder
輸尿管の拡張
abnormal distention of one or both ureters due to accumulation of fluid
輸尿管の閉塞
a partial or total blockage in any part of the ureter causing obstruction of urine flow from the kidney to the urinary bladder; may be congenital, acquired, unilateral, bilateral, acute or chronic
輸尿管狭窄症
abnormal narrowing or constriction of the ureter
